area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-26f8654e3cafcc05255e758578c1151f_r.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "234 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2018015452656268906"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIsJ3G5eumhs4IEAMaCTExODgxOTcxNiC4gu/NBjAAONMCQAJyEzIwMTgwMTU0NTI2NTYyNjg5MDZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1774162415.136406", "card_id": "Q_2018356052123465513", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 78}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "吉林某校老师推出背书攒积分养电子宠物活动，学生为养「宠物」抢着找老师背书，这一教育方式有何启发？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，吉林一老师发布了班级趣味日常，老师推出电子宠物养成激励机制，学生们为不让自己的电子宠物「饿死」，抢着排队找老师背书，学习动力直接拉满！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-dec070076e4e24a793fe47c66da8e1f7_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "198 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2018356052123465513"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIsJ3G5eumhs4IEAMaCTExODgzMjQ1NiDu/PPNBjAAOMABQANyEzIwMTgzNTYwNTIxMjM0NjU1MTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1774162415.136815", "card_id": "Q_2017974362532233492", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "宝妈每天频繁用 84 消毒液消毒患上罕见肺炎，这是什么原因？日常使用 84 消毒液需要注意什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，淮安一名 35 岁女子，生完二胎后为守护宝宝健康，化身「卫生劳模」，每天频繁用 84 消毒液拖地、擦拭家具，没想到竟患上了罕见肺炎。 据了解，女子坚持用 84 消毒约一个月后，开始出现胸闷气喘、呼吸困难的症状，走路五六米就喘不上气，吃药也无好转，随后前往医院就诊。经检查，她被确诊为「急性嗜酸性粒细胞肺炎」——一种发病率仅为十万分之一的罕见病，而致病根源，正是频繁接触 84 消毒液挥发的氯气。 医生解释，84 消毒液主要成分是次氯酸钠，挥发的氯气会刺激呼吸道黏膜，长期暴露可能引发化学性支气管炎、罕见肺炎，甚至呼吸衰竭等严重并发症。目前，女子经对症治疗已好转。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e13afbd503ea6a701efe9bb33fddb390_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "141 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2017974362532233492"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIsJ3G5eumhs4IEAMaCTExODgxNzgwMCD0te7NBjAAOIcBQARyEzIwMTc5NzQzNjI1MzIyMzM0OTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1774162415.137383", "card_id": "Q_2018810613908861913", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 293}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "美以袭击伊朗进入第 23 天，当前局势如何？ 有哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "自美以 2 月 28 日发起对伊朗的军事打击以来，已经过去了三周，伊朗的「真实承诺 -4」反击行动也在 3 月 21 日进入第 72 波。 21 日当天，伊朗的核设施再次遭到袭击，首都德黑兰及伊朗北部、南部多地也持续传出爆炸声。以色列也在当日传出南北方向同时遭袭的消息。 与此同时，美国方面传出消息称已增兵中东，剑指霍尔木兹海峡，而美国总统特朗普则试图把护航该海峡的责任全都甩给盟友。战火燃烧三周 伊朗核设施再遭袭 美军增兵瞄向霍尔木兹海峡"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-bccc91d8f3871e58a71525bd391b36e4_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "136 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2018810613908861913"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIsJ3G5eumhs4IEAMaCTExODg0NzgyOSDGy/rNBjAAOIoGQAVyEzIwMTg4MTA2MTM5MDg4NjE5MTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1774162415.137873", "card_id": "Q_2009985995186148247", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 146}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "普通家庭，补课费一节课 45 分钟 440 元。孩子初一，英语满分 140 考了 50 分，要不要给她补课呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d557175b2f1dd64e8d54c5111db3d4b2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "130 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": 